{"tid":1777052,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2019日本女偶像顏值總選舉排名，繼續坂道天下","createTime":"2019-12-10T03:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T05:26:25.000Z","uid":69115,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"d714f7b4ed9416e4534b174376f214cec85c8af0","tid":1777052,"uid":69115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:01:29.000Z","msg":"舉辦10年的AKB48總選舉是每年日本娛樂圈的大事，不過總選舉在今年停辦了，而廣播節目《レコメン！》每年慣例的「女偶像長相總選舉」（女性アイドル顔だけ総選挙）今年照常舉行。今年果然還是被坂道系列佔領的局面啊...<br />\n20. 長濱ねる （櫸坂46）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rtfY4ZW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrtfY4ZW.jpg&h=39e9ec1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n19.松村沙友理 （乃木坂46)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/10/105117_269c69f5803fa51f3c6d78b84094dd16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F10%2F105117_269c69f5803fa51f3c6d78b84094dd16.jpg&h=f8e1ae86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n18.渡邊理佐（櫸坂46）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKRmij8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrKRmij8.jpg&h=fd6c9edc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n17.生田繪梨花（乃木坂46）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/29gabFa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F29gabFa.jpg&h=36a1119c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n16.寺田蘭世（乃木坂46）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/10/105203_f4dcf7af727914e0a2ec1b320ec65004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F10%2F105203_f4dcf7af727914e0a2ec1b320ec65004.jpg&h=221a77ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n15.渡邊梨加（櫸坂46）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TS4fnM3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTS4fnM3.jpg&h=9ba67eec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n14.鈴本美愉（櫸坂46）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ViH8HM7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FViH8HM7.jpg&h=8a6f7672&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n13. 与田祐希（乃木坂46）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EM740yT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEM740yT.jpg&h=7798310e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n12.小坂菜緒（日向坂46）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pdd7YkB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPdd7YkB.jpg&h=6675b10e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n11.星野南（乃木坂46）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LnMYky0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLnMYky0.jpg&h=97128821&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"287cdb75b4c7c3a4d548c6b5ee24fbe334ca16d4","tid":1777052,"uid":60853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:02:50.000Z","msg":"點解鈴木會高過pe chan???"},{"pid":"3b1a324dc448cbbabb9ca7a9560e66268b8ab6ab","tid":1777052,"uid":69115,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:21:54.000Z","msg":"10.平手友梨奈（櫸坂46） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DdDvWeS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDdDvWeS.jpg&h=7086c53a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9. 松井珠理奈（SKE48）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YDisd1O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYDisd1O.jpg&h=6217b989&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8.齋藤飛鳥（乃木坂46)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e5oLK8B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe5oLK8B.jpg&h=590928fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7. 加藤史帆（日向坂46）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/10/111811_44dda75dfb31ec278baa68c89faeca99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F10%2F111811_44dda75dfb31ec278baa68c89faeca99.jpg&h=e033513e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6.太田夢莉（NMB48）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7AtowO9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7AtowO9.jpg&h=90e2d096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.堀未央奈（乃木坂46）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zo5m2V3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzo5m2V3.jpg&h=35a37621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 鈴木絢音（乃木坂46）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dm7MuBb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDm7MuBb.jpg&h=4bd33fea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.菅井友香（櫸坂46）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dK1dT2Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdK1dT2Y.jpg&h=0f5b23b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 佐佐木琴子（乃木坂46）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x00NYuT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx00NYuT.jpg&h=35bf264d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 白石麻衣（乃木坂46）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bixD491.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbixD491.jpg&h=5f51b5a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白石麻衣以絕對優勢拿下冠軍，這已經是她連續三年登頂這個排行榜，看來只要白麻沒有退役，或者沒有被選為殿堂級，還會繼續稱霸這個排行榜"},{"pid":"423a0ece0b3ae029858169b0bd9c4db519c76e45","tid":1777052,"uid":7311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"287cdb75b4c7c3a4d548c6b5ee24fbe334ca16d4","tid":1777052,"uid":60853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:02:50.000Z","msg":"點解鈴木會高過pe chan???"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:22:44.000Z","msg":"佢叫鈴本"},{"pid":"827ad14ba13c2e1cda0857c506d5f3d160eb0455","tid":1777052,"uid":213300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:23:29.000Z","msg":"白麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2af97c56db3ec61c018e2c0ce02bf4db9341b2","tid":1777052,"uid":60118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20